batch.user_prompt_template:
Generate exactly one premium Korean sentence for high-end typing practice.

[Topic]
- Topic: {topic}

[Tone & Style]
- Style: {style}

[Constraints]
- Length Constraint: The sentence must have exactly around {target_len} Korean characters (excluding spaces and punctuation marks), with a tolerance of ±20 characters.
- Number Constraint: {number_condition}
- Sentence Structure: {complex_sentence}
- Punctuation Constraint: {allowed_punctuation}
- Formatting Constraint: {no_newlines} Output strictly in a single plain text line.

[Critical Instructions]
- {no_quotes}
- {no_proper_nouns}
- Do not output any Markdown code blocks (e.g., do not wrap in ```json or ```text). Output only raw text that satisfies the schema.
- Make sure the sentence is grammatically flawless and has natural spacing in Korean.

topic.user_prompt_template:
Generate exactly 20 diverse, premium Korean sentences for typing practice.

[Topic]
- Topic: "{topic}"

[Constraints per Sentence]
- Length: Each sentence must have exactly around {target_len} Korean characters (excluding spaces and punctuation marks), with a tolerance of ±20 characters.
- Number Constraint: {number_condition}
- Sentence Structure: {complex_sentence}
- Punctuation Constraint: {allowed_punctuation}
- Formatting Constraint: {no_newlines} Output strictly in a single line per sentence.

[Critical Security Instructions]
- {no_quotes}
- {no_proper_nouns}
- You must strictly return the output as a valid JSON object matching the JSON schema: {"sentences": ["sentence1", "sentence2", ...]}.
- Ensure there are no trailing commas or parsing issues. Ensure no markdown formatting is applied to the JSON payload.
